This Application is created for Test Purpose.

//**************************************************
// MARK: - Requirements
//**************************************************
This Application is developed in -
- Xcode - 11.1
- Swift version - 5.0
- iOS Deployment Target - 13.0

//**************************************************
// MARK: - Application Detail
//**************************************************
There are two screen in this app
Screen 1 -
i) It is a login screen.
ii) Having Email and password textfield with Login button.
iii) Is empty validation is added on email and password text field.

Screen 2 -
i) It is showing the list of User Activity.
ii) Having Table view and a logout button on navigation right bar.


//**************************************************
// MARK: - Dependency Used
//**************************************************
In this application, I have used Kingfisher Framework as dependency for showing gif images.
I have used carthage for the dependency framework, using Kingfisher ~> 5.0 version in this app.

//**************************************************
// MARK: - Testing
//**************************************************
Also I have writen one test case for User Activities APi call, in Tests module.

//**************************************************
// MARK: - Assests and icons
//**************************************************
The source of icons used in this app is - "https://icons8.com"

//**************************************************
// MARK: - NOTE
//**************************************************
Commented the print statment of API Request and response.

If you want to print the log on console than need to uncomment the print statments.
Here is the location of the print statments.
1) RequestManager.swift
Line number - 27 & 52

2) APIConfiguration.swift
Line number - 39 & 47

3) XCTestCase+Extension.swift
Line number - 28 & 32
